{"type":"message","id":"255582e6","parentId":"d974351a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T18:59:21.156Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-20 02:59 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 请搜索以下行业的最新动态信息：\n\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\n要求：\n1. 使用 web_search 工具搜索最新信息（2025-2026年的最新动态）\n2. 每个领域搜索1-2条关键信息\n3. 整理成结构化的笔记，包含：标题、来源、关键内容\n4. 输出最终结果"}],"timestamp":1773946761144}}
{"type":"message","id":"8033f016","parentId":"255582e6","timestamp":"2026-03-19T18:59:25.760Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要搜索这四个行业领域的最新动态信息。让我使用web_search工具来搜索每个领域的信息。","thinkingSignature":"9c8b90345260504d4d96a8df1061b025a2a4955679e3bfa979463cb687c93876"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ozpdqlkgn5m0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent && npx @anthropic-ai/claude-code web-search --skill \"miaoda-web-search\" --query \"企业数字化转型 2025最新动态\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"需要使用skill\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":117,"output":110,"cacheRead":18914,"cacheWrite":11868,"totalTokens":31009,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.00013199999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0005674199999999999,"cacheWrite":0.0014241599999999998,"total":0.0021586799999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773946761150}}
